---
title: Jerk Spiced Salmon and Farro Bowl with Pineapple Coleslaw
description: Salmon fillets get a flavour punch with a coating of jerk spices in this balanced bowl. A healthy dose of veggies sweetened with pineapple gets a pick-me-up from lime scented farro. The flavours will take you back to the islands.

